        <abstract> 
<p>Has sent off MS of first part [of <hi rend="italic">Journal of researches</hi>, 2d ed.]. Has so much to add about Fuegians [at beginning of second part] and so much to condense and rewrite in scientific part that he may not have second part ready at end of month; it depends on his health, which is good lately.</p> 
        </abstract>
